Patient preferences for treatment of castration-resistant prostate cancer in 
Japan: a discrete-choice experiment.

Uemura H(1), Matsubara N(2), Kimura G(3), Yamaguchi A(4), Ledesma DA(5), 
DiBonaventura M(6), Mohamed AF(7), Basurto E(6), McKinnon I(6), Wang E(7), 
