(6)Kantar Health, New York, NY, USA.
(7)Bayer Healthcare, Whippany, NJ, USA.
(8)Bayer Yakuhin, Ltd., 2-4-9, Umeda, Kita-ku, Osaka, 530-0001, Japan. 
