'I've Changed My Mind', Mindfulness-Based Childbirth and Parenting (MBCP) for 
pregnant women with a high level of fear of childbirth and their partners: study 
protocol of the quasi-experimental controlled trial.

Veringa IK(1), de Bruin EI(2)(3), Bardacke N(4), Duncan LG(5), van Steensel 
